{"tid":622904,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先飲左杯好耐冇飲過既歇腳亭","createTime":"2018-04-09T13:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T12:14:11.000Z","uid":14036,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f15135bd54e29f4ae9a62b639acdba5b3fb4c60","tid":622904,"uid":14036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"一拎嗰陣都幾驚喜<br />\n啲珍珠勁多<br />\n最衰冇影到<br />\n<br />\n係冇諗過飲完成杯奶茶，又已經食左咁多珍珠都仲淨咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/214457_1b327761c3f1163832e5b9c562e64f72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F214457_1b327761c3f1163832e5b9c562e64f72.png&h=e329c325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從家樂坊對面嗰間收左皮都冇再飲過，其實以而家既珍珠奶茶黎講性價比真係幾高，18蚊咁大杯，奶茶我覺得好飲既，係啲珍珠唔太夠味唔夠甜，勝在幾有咬口又唔硬<br />\n<br />\n好似好打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我垃圾口已經覺得好唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 唔駛同我講天仁茗茶有幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a176886939742436ff47470712571c166fc89a","tid":622904,"uid":187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"好撚大杯屎水"},{"pid":"ecb0bd15a17fa8b828a065ba2e80f9558ae33cb0","tid":622904,"uid":86125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d795d291bbf3e47b8eae351d5e6dda676de32ad8","tid":622904,"uid":27324,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"知自己垃圾口仲開咩post"},{"pid":"24d4dea626e5394b7616f328a04099dad65f80db","tid":622904,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"化學垃圾"},{"pid":"4f48f0ce07c21945e9680176c7df3766caea6800","tid":622904,"uid":46631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"俾狗飲"}]}